name: The Sloppy Drawn Turtle
description: Frank wasn't meant to be perfect. He was drawn in a rush, with wobbly lines and questionable proportions. But that's exactly what makes him special. In a world of polished memes, Frank embraces the chaos. Like any good turtle, Frank takes his time. No rush, no fomo, just vibes. He's here for the long game, building a community of fellow sloppy enthusiasts who appreciate the art of not trying too hard.
